    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-lead-assessor",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification confirms that the 95th-percentile hemolysis index remains below the RH < 1 regulatory threshold across the full input distribution. The model is judged credible for its intended use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions.",
